node.text:
Signature original BBQ ribs & Quesadilla re-plated at home on wood serving board for a pleasant dining. 😊(go to my IG story to see before re-plating).
.

Simply love these fall-off-the-bones pork ribs with a secret marinade that’s cooked low and slow for that tender and flavorful ribs! It’s 💯% satisfactory! .

The Bro Bruce Quesadilla is deliciously served with ranch dip. I reheated it using the airfryer and enjoyed the crisped tortilla with soft melted cheddar cheese and juicy pulled pork much! 😋😋👍.
.

Meat N’ Chill is my to-go place whenever I crave for some good BBQ Ribs. They boasts about their signature pork ribs as the "meanest ribs in town" perfected by Chef Bruce. They also offer a selection of flame-grilled steaks. When they open for dine-in again, I’ll be sure to go back with my foodie buddies! 😍
.

Klook is now offering Meat N’ Chill’s signature dishes, such as Signature Original Pork Ribs, Flame-Grilled Grass-fed Ribeye, Shira XO Beef Ribs, and Wagyu Burger, with islandwide delivery.
.

Do check out Klooksg campaign page at : https://bit.ly/KlooknGoSG and activity page at https://bit.ly/KlookMeatnChill to avail the promotions. .
.
Thank you Meat N Chill for sending this delicious meal and KlookSG for arranging. .
.
.
.
.

@sherbakes Yes super tender, I’d to be really careful when I replate as the meat will drop off the bone anytime! 😅
@teachingpoints Thank you, it’s a really enjoyable meal! The ribs are super tender and delicious! 😋😋😋
@vegkitchensg Thank you! Re-plating the food sure looks more appetizing than consuming it straight from the takeaway or delivery packaging! 😄😋
@baking_taitai agree! And it does take delicate hands and thoughts to plant it so beautifully! 🙌
@vegkitchensg Thank you for your kind words! 😊
@deldeldeldel yes it is really good! This is not my first time eating it. Those who have tried give big thumbs up for it! 👍😋You must try it when you come sg!
Wowww the ribs look really gooood
@dressacake it’s super good! Reasonably priced too! When it opens again, we can go there makan together with @msjaniceeats & @lunchboxmomsg
@makanwarrior Thank you! Looking forward to yours! 😄
@thefatfam_ Yea and it’s so tender good! 😋😋😋
@amily_lovebake me too! Visited the restaurant few times and their set lunch is value for money too!
I love their food ...been there couple of times...young  and talented chef 👨‍🍳
@jo.wonder yes you got to try their signature ribs! It’s so so good! 😋😋👍
@karhingc Meat super tender and drop off the bone so easily! 😋😋😋
@darr3n0ng meanest ribs in town! 😋Got to try!
@mysweetlittletooth Thanks dear! After replating looks more appetizing and yes the quesadillas are really good too, melty cheese and juicy pulled pork! Love it! 😋😋😋
I saw ur Ig story! Really a nice replating u’ve done! 🤩👍🏻 And the quesadillas looks good 😋😋
@sugarylink thank you, replate for a better dining experience at home 😄
@sgfoodtrend yes must try! It’s really good! 💯
Fall of the bone ribs makes us go 🤤
@_boyz86 their ribs are so good, you’ve gotta try! 😋
